    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>Imp</abbr><ex>erator</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Caes</abbr><ex>ar</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arcus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Aur</abbr><ex>elius</ex></expan> <del rend="erasure">Commodus</del> <lb n="2"/>Antoninus <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>ustus</ex></expan> Pius <expan><abbr>Sarm</abbr><ex>aticus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Germ</abbr><ex>anicus</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>pont</abbr><ex>ifex</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>max</abbr><ex>imus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>trib</abbr><ex>unicia</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>pot</abbr><ex>estate</ex></expan> VI <expan><abbr>imp</abbr><ex>erator</ex></expan> IIII co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ul</ex></expan> IIII <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>ater</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>atriae</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/>ripam omnem burgis a solo extructis <lb n="5"/>item praesidi<expan><ex>i</ex><abbr>s</abbr></expan> per loca opportuna <lb n="6"/>ad clandestinos latrunculorum <lb n="7"/>transitus oppositis munivit <lb n="8"/>per <del rend="erasure"><expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucium</ex></expan> Cornelium</del> <lb n="9"/><del rend="erasure">Felicem Plotianum</del> <lb n="10"/><del rend="erasure"><expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>atum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>pr</abbr><ex>o</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>pr</abbr><ex>aetore</ex></expan></del>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Zu Seiten des gerahmten Inschriftfeldes Rankendekor. Datierung: trib.pot. VI / imp. IIII (180 n. Chr.) und cos. IIII (183 n. Chr.) passen nicht zusammen. (B): Mahler: Z. 8-10: [[L(ucium) [Cornelium]]] / [[Felicem P[loti]anum]] / [[leg(atum) pr(o) pr(aetore)]]. Datierung nach S. Soproni (in: Festschrift für Jenő Fitz (Székesfehérvár 1996) 91): Mitte 184 - Mitte 185 n. Chr. Herkunft der Tafel nach Fitz nicht Intercisa, sondern eine der Limesfestungen.</p>
            </div>
